modules.description: Parses multipart/form-data HTTP requests, extracting file and field data. Processes binary file content and textual form fields from HTTP requests. Used to handle user-uploaded files and form data in web applications.

Parses HTTP multipart/form-data streams, extracting field names, content types, filenames, and part bodies from a given boundary. Processes input incrementally using a reader, returning parsed parts or leftover data after parsing completes. Supports direct access to part headers and their parameters for handling form submissions and file uploads.
